  m_text: "Please raise your hands in the position indicated in the picture. \nYour
    palms should face the camera, your arms bent at the \nelbows and not far from
    your face.  Make sure your fingers are \ncompletely stretched out. Also, make
    sure your thumbs stick out \nto the sides and are not pressed against your palms.
    Once the \ncalibration is complete, you can move your hands freely.\nIf you have
    read these instructions and are ready to begin \ncalibration, click \"Close\"."
